sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>(JupyterLab/CodeServer/RStudio)<br/>8888/TCP or 8787/TCP HTTP
    participant NGINX as NGINX Proxy<br/>(CodeServer/RStudio only)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Elyra as Elyra Pipeline Editor<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as KFP API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Runtime as Runtime Image Pod<br/>(headless)
    participant DB as User Databases<br/>(MongoDB/MSSQL/PostgreSQL)
    participant PyPI as PyPI / CRAN<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,PyPI: Flow 1: User Accesses Jupyter Workbench

    User->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: OIDC/OAuth
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>HTTPRoute<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>validates user identity
    KRBAC->>Notebook: HTTP/8888<br/>pod-local<br/>Auth: None
    Notebook-->>KRBAC: JupyterLab UI
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,PyPI: Flow 1b: User Accesses CodeServer/RStudio Workbench

    User->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: OIDC/OAuth
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>HTTPRoute<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>NGINX: HTTP/8080<br/>pod-local<br/>Auth: None
    NGINX->>Notebook: HTTP/8787<br/>reverse proxy<br/>Auth: None
    Notebook-->>NGINX: IDE UI
    NGINX-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,PyPI: Flow 2: Notebook to Kubernetes API

    Notebook->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Notebook: API Response

    Note over User,PyPI: Flow 3: User installs packages

    Notebook->>PyPI: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>pip install / R install.packages
    PyPI-->>Notebook: Package artifacts

    Note over User,PyPI: Flow 4: User connects to databases

    Notebook->>DB: Various ports<br/>(27017/1433/5432)<br/>Auth: User credentials
    DB-->>Notebook: Query results

    Note over User,PyPI: Flow 5: Pipeline Runtime Execution

    Elyra->>KFP: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KFP->>Runtime: Creates Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    Runtime->>Runtime: Executes pipeline node
    Runtime-->>KFP: Execution result
